full_text:
Trimmers are usually used to fine-tune the frequency range. If the
varactor has enough range by itself, you probably don&#39;t need the
trimmer.

Otherwise, you&#39;d probably want to set the trimmer at the bottom of the
broadcast band with the voltage across the varactor at minimum.

Zack


